Please view "INSTALL" for more information.

if you are performing an update from Centreon-2.0.1 or an older version:
Once the web update finished, you will have to execute follow the steps bellow to rebuild Centreon reporting statistics :
1) 	Modify the logs retention period in Centreon interface : Administration > Options > Centstorage > Options > Logs retention duration
	The retention duration must cover the oldest nagios log archive file in the folder nagios/var/archives/

2) 	then execute the following command lines in Centreon folder :
	# ./bin/logAnalyser -a
	# ./cron/archiveDayLog -r

3) reset the logs retention period to the previous value
